  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 3. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Full 13-factor assessment: 10 factors assessed, 3 factors flagged as beyond current project scope and therefore not assessed. Decision recorded as Accepted despite unassessed factors at elevated model risk.",
